posts.title: How to change address in voter ID card
posts.text:
The Election Commission of India (ECI) has made the process of updating your address in your voter ID card a very simple process. Instead of filling different forms and following various protocols, you can do it all with just one single application form. 

Changing your residential address on your voter ID card can easily be done by submitting an application form along with the proof of your present address to the Election Officer of your particular constituency. 

Known as transposing of name from electoral list, your name will be shifted from your old constituency's electoral list to the new one, with all your details retained. 

For the convenience of voters in order to change their addresses on their voter ID cards, the ECI has introduced an online application process. 

Steps to change your address in voter ID card online: 

* Log on to the official website available for voters the National Voters Services Portal by clicking on http://www.nvsp.in 

* Select the "Apply online for registration of new voter/due to shifting from AC" option. 

* Choose Form 8A from the available options provided, after which an online form will appear in a new tab. 

* Fill in the details as required, including your name and address, state, constituency and also your new address. 

* Upload a document that mentions your current address (such as Aadhaar card, bank pass book or any official document) 

* Once you have filled and uploaded the documents, submit the form online. 

* You will receive a reference number, which can be used by you to track your application online. 

* After you have submitted your application, it will be verified by the electoral officers. 

On successful verification, you will receive your voter ID card with your present address mentioned.

posts.title: Νέα μαρτυρία για τη δολοφονία στο Β' Νεκροταφείο - Ποια είναι τα επιπλέον στοιχεία
posts.text:
Καθημερινά νέες πληροφορίες βλέπουν το φως της δημοσιότητας αναφορικά με την υπόθεση της στυγερής δολοφονίας της εφοριακού Δώρας Ζέμπερη. Πλέον οι αστυνομικοί οδηγούνται 
όλο και πιο κοντά στο ενδεχόμενο της ληστείας μιας και δίπλα από το γεμάτο αίμα της σώμα έλειπαν η τσάντα της και το κινητό της τηλέφωνο. 

Όπως μετέδωσε ο Alpha στο κεντρικό του δελτίο ειδήσεων χθες, μία νέα μαρτυρία μπορεί να δώσει νέα επιπλέον στοιχεία για το αποτρόπαιο έγκλημα. Λίγες μέρες πριν δολοφονηθεί η νεαρή εφοριακός, 30 μέτρα από εκείνο το σημείο, μία άλλη γυναίκα είχε ζήσει τον τρόμο.

Η γυναίκα ήταν στο μνήμα του συζύγου της πολύ κοντά στο σημείο, φροντίζοντας τον τάφο όταν ένας νεαρός άνδρας την πλησίασε και επιχείρησε να της αρπάξει την τσάντα. Το περιστατικό έχει ήδη γίνει γνωστό στην αστυνομία και όταν εκείνη κατήγγειλε την επίθεση στους φύλακες του Β’ Νεκροταφείου εκείνοι της απάντησαν πως πρόκειται για γνωστό τοξικομανή.

Στο περιστατικό αναφέρθηκε και ο δικηγόρος του πατέρα της Δώρας Ζέμπερη, Απόστολος Λύτρας, λέγοντας πως «από τον Σεπτέμβρη είχε γίνει γνωστή η απόπειρα ληστείας σε κοντινό της δολοφονίας, σημείο. Εγώ ενημέρωσα τις αρχές για αυτή την πληροφορία να την αξιολογήσει και προφανώς να καλέσει το θύμα να καταθέσει».

Η γυναίκα στην κατάθεσή της στη αστυνομία ανέφερε πως ο άνδρας είχε ύψος περίπου 1,75 ήταν καστανός, μιλούσε ελληνικά και απομακρύνθηκε από την είσοδο του νεκροταφείου.

Όπως αποκαλύπτει το ρεπορτάζ, η Αστυνομία ξεψαχνίζει το υλικό από τις κάμερες και της οδού Αχαρνών στην οποία ενδεχομένως να πέρασε ή να κατέληξε ο δράστης και κοιτούν για οποιονδήποτε μπορεί να κινούταν ύποπτα.

Την ίδια στιγμή σαρώνουν τις περιοχές της Ομόνοιας και την Αχαρνών οι αστυνομικοί, ακολουθώντας τα ίχνη του δολοφόνου της Δώρας Ζέμπερη.

Καλούν, μάλιστα, εκ νέου μάρτυρες που είχαν καταθέσει από τις πρώτες κιόλας μέρες της δολοφονίας, για συμπληρωματικές καταθέσεις, πιστεύοντας ότι μέσα από τα λόγια τους δεν αποκλείεται να εντοπίσουν αυτό το στοιχείο κλειδί που θα τους οδηγήσει στον δολοφόνο της Δώρας.

Είναι χαρακτηριστικό ότι, μεταξύ των ατόμων που έχουν κληθεί να καταθέσουν, είναι ακόμα και η ψυχοθεραπεύτρια που έβλεπε η Δώρα τον τελευταίο καιρό.

این جشنواره در محورهای خودرو و فرهنگ رانندگی، خودرو، محیط زیست و هوای پاک، خودرو و خانواده و خودرو و ورزش در رشته های عکس و کارتون برگزار می شود. 
رشته عکس در ۲ بخش حرفه ای و مردمی برگزار می شود که در بخش حرفه ای عکاسان و علاقمندان می توانند آثار خود را بر اساس موضوعات فراخوان، به صورت تک عکس و همچنین مجموعه ارسال کنند.

posts.title: Himachal Pradesh Assembly Elections: Know your constituency
posts.text:
The Right to Vote is one of the biggest strengths a citizen has in a democracy. So to practice this right a voter must be completely aware and informed about the provisions available to him/her by the government of the country. 

For those who wish to and who are eligible to cast their votes in the upcoming Himachal Pradesh elections can know their respective constituency by following these simple steps: 

* Visit the web page http://himachal.nic.in 

* On the homepage click on the ninth option which says "Know your Constituency" 

* A new window with the Title "Know your Constituency" will open. 

* Select your district from the dropdown that is available on the right-hand side under the title "Select District" 

* On the left-hand side is the option of "Locality/Colony Name" wherein you will have to manually enter your locality. 

* After entering the details click on the "Search" tab 

Your respective constituency will now appear in front of you.

posts.author: vestact (noreply@blogger.com)
posts.title: Apple in Paradise
posts.text:
To market to market to buy a fat pig. The Paradise Papers will be a talking point for the coming weeks as more details emerge. The latest big name revealed is Apple, who went 'tax haven shopping' after their setup in Ireland ran into issues - ( Apple had five burning questions about the best tax haven for its billions ). These multinational companies spend millions to ensure that they are structuring their tax affairs legally. The problem is that tax codes can be open to interpretation, as seen with Apple and Ireland. The EU feels that Apple pushed things too far and should pay Ireland $13 billion, Ireland is appealing the decision. When a country doesn't want $13 billion in tax revenues, you know how subjective tax codes can be. 

As I said on CNBC yesterday, it is management's job to pay as little tax as possible legally, and it is government's job to decide what the tax codes should be. The problem for governments at the moment is the ambiguity in the way tax codes and treaties that have been drawn up. Loop holes are being closed and standardisation of definitions are being implemented. We have also seen that large financial institutions have had pressure put on them not to do business with entities linked to tax havens. If you want to read further about the initial names linked to the papers, here is a brief summary - Here's a guide to the major revelations in the Paradise Papers . What is interesting to me is how many of the 'big guns' are intertwined in many business deals. 

Market Scorecard. Our market powered through the 60 000 mark yesterday on the open, meaning it has taken just under 3-years to climb 20% from 50 000 points to 60 000. The Dow was up 0.04%, the S&P 500 was up 0.13%, the Nasdaq was up 0.33% and the All-share was up 0.57%/ . Lonmin was down another 5.9% yesterday, but after being one of the best-performing stocks for October it is still trading higher than it was in September. 



Company corner 

Byron's Beats 

Last week we received third-quarter numbers from Cerner which disappointed the market. The share dropped 9% on the news as forward guidance was revised down. We should put that drop into perspective. Even after that fall, the share price is up 38% so far this year. It all depends on where you draw the line in the sand. Having said that, this has been a volatile ride. This business is a high margin software company with high expectations. A volatile ride usually comes with that package. 

Bookings for the quarter came in at $1.1bn. This was much lower than expectations because a few large contracts will now only be included in the fourth quarter numbers. When these bookings reflect, it should result in an all-time high bookings for the full year . It has been a good year with some big government institutions signing up for their healthcare software services. 

Revenues came in at $1.276bn which was 8% higher than the comparative quarter ; $928 million of that came from support, maintenance and services. You can see that this is a retention business. Once you have signed up a hospital or an institution, their annuity business is a key driver of Cerner's future profits. 

Another important factor to note is that only $142 million of these revenues came from outside the US. The potential to expand globally is massive . 

Earnings for the year are expected to come in at around $2.42 per share, putting the company at 27 times forward earnings. The business does have gross margins of 83% and very impressive cash flows which explains the high multiple somewhat. 

We remain buy rated on this stock as it continues to secure solid government contracts in the US. We will do a more detailed analysis of the full year when those numbers come out next quarter. 



Linkfest, lap it up 

One thing, from Paul 

The biggest aggregate client position in our New York business is Apple . Not surprising really, because it is a must-own stock and has done really well in recent months. The total value of our Apple holding at Fidelity Clearing & Custody Solutions (where the shares are held in safe custody) is $15.1 million. 

At its current share price of $174.25, Apple has a market value of just a whisker over $900 billion. That makes it the most valuable listed company in the world. It is the first time that any listed company has breached that mark. Well done Tim Cook. Onwards to $1 trillion! 

The reason that the stock is trading so well is that this coming holiday season will probably be the biggest ever, as shoppers go mad for its new iPhone X. Those have the new larger OLED screens and cost over $1,000 each. They are selling out as they hit the stores, but Apple's formidable production system will soon have them available for sale around the world. 

This article provides some updates on the opening iPhone X weekend - Apple iPhone X draws lines, and some activation errors on AT&T and Verizon services 



Michael's Musings 

We sometimes forget how massive China really is . The following graphic shows how China's biggest 31 cities are a similar size to certain countries - 31 Chinese Cities With Economies as Big as Countries . 



A question that is as important as when to buy is when to sell . Given that we are not market timers, and don't try jump in and out of the market, we look to sell when something has fundamentally changed at the company - The Question of When to Sell Isn't So Simple . The last point that Barry makes is important, even a well-timed sell and then corresponding buy can be break-even at best due to taxes and transaction costs. How much does a stock need to drop before your losses would be more than the taxes and costs incurred in selling? 



Bright's Banter 

One of my favourite quotes from Howard Marks taken straight from his book The Most Important Thing 

"When people say flatly, 'we only buy A' or 'A is a superior asset class,' that sounds a lot like 'we'd buy A at any price; and we'd buy it before B, C or D at any price.' That just has to be a mistake. No asset class or investment has the birthright of a high return. It's only attractive if it's priced right. 

Hopefully, if I offered to sell you my car, you'd ask the price before saying yes or no. Deciding on an investment without carefully considering the fairness of its price is just as silly. But when people decide without disciplined consideration of valuation that they want to own something, as they did with tech stocks in the late 1990s---or that they simply won't own something, as they did with junk bonds in the 1970s and early 1980s---that's just what they're doing. 

Bottom line: there's no such thing as a good or bad idea regardless of price! " 
In the following article, Howard Marks explains why passive investing is not the silver bullet you have been looking for! - Howard Marks On Passive Investing 



Home again, home again, jiggety-jog. Tencent is up over 3% in Hong Kong, expect a raging Naspers when the bell goes at 9:00 our time! There is CPI data out of the EU around lunch time and then this afternoon, the JOLTs number from the US. As the US reaches full employment, the JOLTs data becomes more important.

Eli eli, oma 2006 330xi tällä N52 padalla on nyt välillä vilkutellut tuota moottorivaloa ja vikakoodiksi antaa näitä vanoksen säätöjen alueen ulkopuolella oloja. Täältä ja ulkomaisilta foorumeilta saanut sen käsityksen, että homma olisi hyvä aloittaa noiden solenoidin putsauksella tai vaihtamisella.
Te ketkä näitä olette vaihtaneet, mitä olette laittaneet tilalle? Orggis osa näyttäisi olevan 150e/kpl. Ainakin schmiedmann myy tarviketta sitten puoleen hintaan tästä. Ja Ebaysta kun katsoo, niin sieltä löytyy sitten halvimmat jo 50e/pari. Eli aika isoa haarukkaa.
Onko joku ajanut näillä tarvikkeilla onnistuneesti, vai onko parempi pitäytyä taatusti toimivassa? Näiden vaihtaminenhan ei onneksi iso homma ole, että sinänsä voi vaikka kokeilla vähän kepillä jäätä... Yhdessä tapauksessa pohdittiin samaa asiaa.... kunnes löydettiin netistä kokemuksia noista kiinalaisista jotka eivät toimi. Älä haaskaa rahojasi niihin koska lopputulos on sellainen että ostat alkuperäiset. Kinukeissa toimimattomuuden lisäksi on ollut porauksia sivussa josta on voinut tunnistaa että jotain on pielessä. Aidon ja kopion tunnistaa osan väristä (kiinnitysosa hiekkapuhallettu vs kiiltävä) sekä hinnasta ja varaosanron puuttumisena... jokainen toki tekee rahoillaan mitä haluaa...

Здание UNESCO в Париже. Фото Google
 
Лиза Юдин  
Париж. Осень 2017-го.
39-я Генеральная ассамблея ЮНЕСКО. Как только эти шесть букв появились, любому израильтянину понятно, о чем речь пойдет. Конечно, об очередной антиизраильской резолюции. А что еще может быть? 
Уже много лет ЮНЕСКО, как впрочем, и другие АБВГДейки ооновского разлива больше ничем не занимается. На сей раз нас были намерены осудить за плохое состояние школ на «оккупированных территориях», включающих в себя “по ихнему” – Иудею, Самарию, Голанские высоты.
Итак, осенний Париж. Прогулки по “рю” и бульварам, кафе, бистро и Булонский лес.
Народ на ассамблею валил валом. Отдых и культурное времяпровождение, да еще не за свой счет.
А что? Как всегда, вынесли резолюцию на обсуждение, без всяких дебатов быстренько проголосовали скопом за все про все. Израиль. Чего обсуждать? И так все ясно – агрессор, оккупант, апартеид, расизм и всякие прочие синонимы.

10-15 минут и вперед, навстречу Монмартру и Монпарнасу. Искрится в бокалах бургундское, еще не зачерствели бриоши…
Облом. Крах мечт (или мечтов?) и вожделений. Я бы даже сказала, полная ж..а случилась. Выдохлось на этот раз и бургундское, и изделия провинций Шампань и Пуату. Покрылись неаппетитной сухой коркой бриоши и всякие другие изыски знаменитой французской кухни. Не дождались клиентов ни прекрасные цветочницы, ни дамы света, ни дамы полусвета. Как проклятые заседали они, заседали и заседали…
Представитель США в UNESCO Крис Хигдорн
 
Короче, полный облом. Теперь я понимаю, почему нас так не любят в сим заведении – делегации Израиля и США, пользуясь положениями устава, потребовали номинального голосования всех 196 государств, входящих в организацию.

Вы представляете, что это такое?! Персональное голосование по каждому из 11 параграфов резолюции! С участием всех стран! Вы представляете, сколько времени займет такая процедура? Председательствующий называет каждую страну, выслушивает ответ ее председателя и заносит ответ в протокол.
Короче, через три часа народ занервничал, Конца-краю не предвиделось и близко. Объявили перерыв. Кое-как подкрепившись, без всякого аппетита, делегации вернулись в зал. Попробовали бы не вернуться! Все предыдущее пошло бы насмарку.
И тут первый сюрприз. Китай голосует против резолюции. Впервые за всю историю присутствия в ООН. То ли китайцам надоела вся эта тягомотина, проголосовать “против” быстрее, чем “за” – “за” надо долго и нудно объяснять позицию; то ли что-то они для себя уяснили, но факт – Китай проголосовал против антиизраильской резолюции.
В зале шок. Делегация ПА нервно теребит куфии и уже прикидывает стоимость туннеля из Газы в Пекин.
Второй шок. Мексика голосует против резолюции. Тоже впервые за всю историю поддерживает Израиль. Видать, в благодарность за недавнюю помощь при землетрясении.
И это не все. Еще несколько стран изменили своей традиции автоматической поддержки ПА.
Куфии уже не просто теребят, в них уже открыто сморкаются, наиболее “пламенные” уголками вытирают слезы…
Премьера окончена, можно сказать – удалась! Еще пару-тройку столь многочасовых бдений и, глядишь, у некоторых прыти поубавится. Во всяком случае, “быстренько и на свободу” больше не получится. Все, как требует Устав.

芳根はオファーを受けた時の心境を「本当にわたしが!? とただただびっくりしました」と振り返りつつ、「やるとなったら、めいっぱい楽しんでこの冬はクラゲ色に染まりたいです！」と意気込みを明かす。今作での役作りについては「力を入れず純粋に月海という女の子として全力で生きて、原作の面白さを引き出していけるよう、監督や共演者の方、スタッフの皆さんと力を合わせて頑張りたいです」と語っている。 原作の書影 
原作者の東村は今回の発表にあたり「ドラマ化のお話をいただいた時、こんな変な漫画が月9になるんか!? とびっくりしましたが、めちゃくちゃうれしかったです」とコメント。「芳根さんのメガネ＆おさげ、本当に楽しみです！」と続けている。（編集部・海江田宗）

건강정보 얼굴 울긋불긋… 나도 '안면홍조'일까? 1시간 전 URL 복사 본문 기타 기능 번역보기 http://blog.naver.com/kkbej/221134675504 안면홍조를 예방, 완화하려면 평소 햇빛노출, 급격한 온도변화, 감정변화를 최대한 피하는 게 도움이 된다./사진=헬스조선 DB
평소에도 얼굴이 울긋불긋하거나, 조금만 긴장해도 얼굴이 빨개지는 사람들이 있다. 이럴 때는 '안면홍조'를 의심해야 한다. 안면홍조는 얼굴, 목 부위 피부가 붉게 변하면서 열감이 나타나는 것이다. 보통 2~4분 지속되는데 하루에도 여러 번 나타날 수 있다.
안면홍조 유발 원인은 급격한 감정 변화, 음주, 뜨거운 물로 하는 목욕 등이다. 이로 인해 얼굴 혈관이 확장되면서 피부가 빨갛게 보인다. 심해지면 목이나 가슴 등 여러 부위로 증상이 퍼진다. 더 문제인 것은 이를 방치했을 때 혈관이 늘어나고 피부 내 염증이 악화되면서 만성 염증성 피부질환으로 이어질 수 있다는 것이다.
따라서 조기에 치료하는 게 좋다. 우선 먹는 약이나 바르는 연고를 써볼 수 있는데, 가장 흔히 쓰이는 것이 항생제다. 안면홍조가 있는 피부를 검사하면 염증에 의해 혈관이 많이 확장돼 있기 때문에, 항생제로 이 염증을 없애는 식이다. 이 밖에 비타민A유도체나 항안드로겐성 제제, 베타차단제 등의 전문의약품 등이 쓰일 수 있다. 약으로도 증상이 낫지 않으면 IPL이나 PDL 등 혈관을 수축시키는 레이저 치료를 고려한다.
평소에는 피부 자극을 줄이도록 노력하는 게 중요하다. 햇빛노출, 급격한 온도변화와 감정변화, 무분별한 화장품 사용을 피하는 게 도움이 된다. 뜨거운 사우나나 찜질방을 자제하고, 특히 주부들의 경우 뜨거운 불 위에서 오래 요리하지 말아야 한다. 뜨거운 열이 혈관을 확장시키기 때문이다. 화장품은 이것저것 쓰기보다 저자극성 보습제를 바르는 것을 기본으로 하는 게 안전하다.

PURWAKARTA,RAKA -  Peraturan daerah (Perda) tentang Kesehatan Jiwa yang saat ini tengah digodok oleh pansus V DPRD Provinsi Jawa Barat, tidak lama lagi bakal segera rampung. Hal ini seperti disampaikan oleh anggota Komisi V DPRD Jawa Barat H Rustandie SH. 
"Perda Kesehatan Jiwa ini menjadi penting, karena masih kurangnya sarana prasarana yang mendukung penanganan pasien dengan gangguan kesehatan jiwa. Di Provinsi Jawa Barat, saja baru ada satu rumah sakit jiwa (RSJ), yakni RSJ Cisarua. Pun halnya dengan masih kurangnya SDM dokter spesialis jiwa. Di Purwakarta misalnya, hanya ada seorang," kata Rustandi, di Purwakarta belum lama ini.
Rustandie juga menilai, pemahaman masyarakat masih minim terkait gangguan kesehatan jiwa. "Masih banyak yang menganggap ini guna-guna, bukannya dibawa ke rumah sakit jiwa malah ke tempat lain yang tidak seharusnya," ujarnya.
Dengan adanya Perda Kesehatan Jiwa, sambun dia, maka setiap rumah sakit umum daerah harus memiliki 10 bed khusus untuk pasien kesehatan jiwa. "Perda tersebut juga akan memudahkan kerja sama dengan Yayasan Mentari Hati Kota Tasikmalaya pimpinan Dadang Heryadi atau yayasan sejenis lainnya," kata Rustandie.
Selain itu, dengan terwujudnya Perda Kesehatan Jiwa, kata dia, tidak ada lagi kasus kurangnya obat-obatan dan tenaga kesehatan. "Bahkan dalam perda tersebut juga akan menyediakan beasiswa pendidikan dokter spesialis jiwa," pungkasnya. (gan)

posts.title: U Leskovcu se slavi 100 godina Oktobarske revolucije
posts.text:
Jedini grad u Srbiji koji obeleava ovaj datum FOTO: Panoramio/D. Kovačević „Ako je Kraljevska akademija u Londonu uvrstila u svoju aktivnost ovih dana obeležavanje 100 godina Oktobarske revolucije, ako je to urađeno i na Menhetnu, možemo i mi u Leskovcu da damo i naše viđenje.
Smatramo se pozvanim da na taj način obeležimo taj jedan od najznačajniji događaja u istorji radničkog pokreta sveta, jer od tada na ovamo nikada više nije bilo isto“, kazao je dana lider PS Božidar Vučković u Leskovcu i koordinator obeležavanja godišnjice.
Živan Stojković istoričar je kazao da misli da je Leskovac jedini grad u Srbiji koji obeležava radnički pokret sveta.
Za ovu priliku formiran je Organizacioni odbor kojeg pored Vučkovića čine i dr Živan Stojković, Predrag Dimitrijević, Strahinja Nikolić, Dragan Milovanović i dr Veselin Petrović.
Tako će se u utorak u 10 časova položiti venac na spomenik Blagoja Nikolića, Leskovčanina koji je učestvovao u Oktobraskoj revoluciji, bio Lenjinov saborac i komandovao jednim odredom u jurišu na Zimski dvorac u Peterburgu.
Istoga dana u 11 časova biće otvorena izložba „1917-2017“, a potom i tribina.
Planira se i formiranje Rusko-srpskog prijateljstva, pa će s tim u vezi 15. novembra u leskovačkom pozorištu biti održano veče sa prigodnim programom gde će se obeležiti, rekao je Vučković, tradicionalno prijateljstvo ruskog i srpskog naroda, a kontakti su uspostavljeni i sa ambasadom Rusije u Srbiji.
Oktobarska revolucja počela je 25 . oktobra po starom, 7. novermbra 1917. Godine po novom. Bio je to krvavi građanski rat usred Prvog svetskog rata.

/ Gare aux coupures de courant cet hiver ENERGIE Gare aux coupures de courant cet hiver Photo d'illustration Julio Pelaez Partager cette info Le gestionnaire du réseau électrique RTE a prévenu mardi qu’il pourrait être amené à prendre des mesures "exceptionnelles", allant jusqu’à des coupures programmées cet hiver, pour assurer l’alimentation des foyers français. 
Alors que l'hiver s'est déjà abattu sur la France, le gestionnaire du réseau électrique français annonce ce mardi de possibles restrictions d'électricité dans les mois à venir, pouvant aller jusqu'à des coupures programmées. 
Des arrêts de centrales non prévus ou des conditions climatiques hors normes "pourraient fragiliser l’alimentation électrique des Français" pendant les mois les plus froids, indique RTE dans son bilan prévisionnel. La sécurité d’approvisionnement électrique du pays est particulièrement sensible l’hiver, du fait de la place importante de l’électricité dans le chauffage des Français. Coupures tournantes 
L’offre de production énergétique sera supérieure à celle de l’hiver dernier, lorsqu’un nombre important de centrales nucléaires d’EDF avait été fermé, souligne RTE. Toutefois, le gestionnaire du réseau a placé l’hiver qui arrive "sous surveillance", signifiant qu’il nécessitera une vigilance particulière. 
Les mesures exceptionnelles qui pourraient être prises sont l’interruption de l’alimentation de gros consommateurs industriels volontaires ou encore une baisse de 5% de la tension sur les réseaux électriques. En tout dernier recours, RTE pourrait décider de coupures de courant momentanées, localisées et tournantes.   10:20 | Mis à jour il y a environ 1 heures |
